        "timestamp": "2018-09-11 13:41:15.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: -Code-Review\n\nHello OOM team, this probably should be merged into beijing sooner rather than later, beijing will be broken until then.\n\nRoot cause seems to be commit 19e44947f0592e8e36206fe1c4cefc48c428c26a that merged some AAI changes from master back into Beijing, but with the side effects to pull in a bunch of other changes for other ONAP components including policy (sdc, sdnc, portal, ..).   Not sure if there are any issues with the port of those other components, but there will be certainly issues for policy as Silvius reported.",
